subconscious sexual attraction!

13:07.102 --> 13:08.235
Are you sure?

13:08.303 --> 13:10.054
Do you want me
to get the book?!

13:10.055 --> 13:11.255
No, no, no, Frasier,
Frasier, Frasier,

13:11.256 --> 13:12.422
Frasier, forget the book!

13:12.423 --> 13:15.592
Frasier,
listen to me. I...

